{"id":340006,"date":[{"year":1957,"month":1,"day":5}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"222","ytitle":"","mtitle":"黎明的海港","ftitle":"","authors":["吴荫循"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴荫循"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驶近了月色朦胧的海港，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那熟悉的灯塔又在迎接我们；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她闪烁如亲人的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲切而又温存。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的海港还在沉睡:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清风送过来低柔的潮声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海波摇乱了微明的灯影……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我像个被晨风吹醒的丈夫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看美丽的妻子怀抱婴儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用微笑诉说一个甜美的梦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵风从东方吹来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着一个灿烂的黎明……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一队渔船载着丰收归来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻柔的桨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇醒了海港轻柔的梦……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渐渐地，天空变得明亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溶尽了启明星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤凰树舒展青枝迎接朝阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绽开了新的红英……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1956年9月-12月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汕头—北京"}]}